Quarter: The fiscal quarter and year for which the warranty claim resolution rate is reported (e.g., 'Q3 2025').
Resolution_Rate: The percentage of warranty claims resolved within one week for the specified quarter, indicating the efficiency of the customer service team.
Customer_Experience_Impact: A qualitative assessment of how the resolution rate affects customer experience and satisfaction, relevant for strategic planning by the Customer Service Team Lead.
